---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CtaBanner from '../components/CtaBanner.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Free SEO Audit | Find Out Why You're Not Ranking on Google | DC technolabs"
  description="Get a free SEO audit from DC technolabs. We analyse your keyword rankings, backlinks, technical SEO, and local visibility. Free report in 48 hours. No obligation."
  canonical="https://dctechnolabs.in/free-seo-audit"
>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO + FORM
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-audit-hero" id="seo-audit-form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="seo-audit-grid">

      <!-- Left: Content -->
      <div class="seo-audit-content">
        <span class="section-label">Free SEO Audit</span>
        <h1>Find Out Exactly <span class="highlight">Why You're Not on Page 1</span></h1>
        <p>Your competitors are ranking above you. There's a specific reason why, and it's fixable. We'll find it, explain it in plain language, and show you exactly what needs to change. Completely free.</p>

        <div class="seo-audit-includes">
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">📊</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Keyword Rankings Report</strong>
              <p>Where you currently rank for your most important business keywords</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">🔗</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Backlink Profile Analysis</strong>
              <p>The quality and quantity of sites linking to you vs your top competitors</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">⚙️</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Technical SEO Health Check</strong>
              <p>Crawl errors, indexing issues, site structure, and Core Web Vitals</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">📍</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Local SEO Assessment</strong>
              <p>Google Business Profile, local citations, and Google Maps ranking potential</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">🏆</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Competitor Gap Analysis</strong>
              <p>What your top 3 competitors are doing that you're not, and how to close the gap</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="seo-include-item">
            <div class="seo-include-icon">📋</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Priority Action Plan</strong>
              <p>The top 5 things to fix first, ranked by impact on your rankings</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="seo-proof-bar">
          <span>✓ 945+ audits completed</span>
          <span>✓ Delivered within 48 hours</span>
          <span>✓ No obligation, no sales pressure</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Form -->
      <div class="seo-audit-form-card">
        <h2>Get Your Free SEO Audit</h2>
        <p>Fill in your details and we'll send a complete SEO report within 48 hours.</p>
        <form
          class="seo-audit-form"
          id="seoAuditForm"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="0141be72-7ed9-4e67-bd38-e0154c164ba6" />
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Free SEO Audit Request - DC technolabs" />

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-name">Your Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="seo-name" name="name" placeholder="Priya Shah" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-phone">WhatsApp / Phone *</label>
            <input type="tel" id="seo-phone" name="phone" placeholder="+91 98765 43210" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="seo-email" name="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-website">Website URL *</label>
            <input type="url" id="seo-website" name="website" placeholder="https://yourwebsite.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-city">Your City *</label>
            <select id="seo-city" name="city" required>
              <option value="">Select your city</option>
              <option>Ahmedabad</option>
              <option>Gandhinagar</option>
              <option>Surat</option>
              <option>Vadodara</option>
              <option>Rajkot</option>
              <option>Other Gujarat city</option>
              <option>Outside Gujarat</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-keywords">3 Keywords You Want to Rank For</label>
            <input type="text" id="seo-keywords" name="target_keywords" placeholder="e.g. dental clinic Satellite, dentist Ahmedabad" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="seo-competitor">Your Main Competitor Website (optional)</label>
            <input type="url" id="seo-competitor" name="competitor" placeholder="https://competitorwebsite.com" />
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
            Get My Free SEO Audit →
          </button>
          <p class="form-reassurance">Report delivered to your email in 48 hours. Zero obligation.</p>
          <div id="seoAuditFormMsg" class="form-msg" style="display:none"></div>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: TRUST BAR
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-trust-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="seo-trust-inner">
      <div class="seo-trust-item">
        <div class="seo-trust-num">780+</div>
        <div class="seo-trust-label">SEO Audits Done</div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="seo-trust-item">
        <div class="seo-trust-num">4.9/5</div>
        <div class="seo-trust-label">Client Rating</div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="seo-trust-item">
        <div class="seo-trust-num">48 hrs</div>
        <div class="seo-trust-label">Guaranteed Delivery</div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="seo-trust-item">
        <div class="seo-trust-num">100%</div>
        <div class="seo-trust-label">No Obligation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-trust-divider"></div>
      <div class="seo-trust-item">
        <div class="seo-trust-num">7+</div>
        <div class="seo-trust-label">Years in Ahmedabad</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 3: THE SEO AUDIT COVERS
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-covers reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Full Coverage</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Every Component of Your SEO Analysed</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="seo-covers-grid">

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">📈</div>
        <h3>Keyword Ranking Analysis</h3>
        <p>We check your current ranking positions for your industry's most valuable keywords, both the ones you're targeting and the ones you should be.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Current keyword positions</li>
          <li>Traffic potential per keyword</li>
          <li>Ranking vs competitors comparison</li>
          <li>Quick-win keywords (position 5–20)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h3>Technical SEO Audit</h3>
        <p>The invisible factors that either help or hurt your rankings, site structure, crawlability, indexing, and the signals Google looks at before ranking any page.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Crawl errors and blocked pages</li>
          <li>Indexing status report</li>
          <li>Canonical tag issues</li>
          <li>Site speed (Core Web Vitals)</li>
          <li>XML sitemap quality</li>
          <li>Schema markup presence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">📝</div>
        <h3>On-Page SEO Review</h3>
        <p>How well each page is optimized for its target keyword, the factors you can control directly on your website.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Title tag quality per page</li>
          <li>Meta description optimization</li>
          <li>Header tag hierarchy</li>
          <li>Content depth and keyword coverage</li>
          <li>Internal linking structure</li>
          <li>Image optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">🔗</div>
        <h3>Backlink Profile</h3>
        <p>The strength and quality of your off-page authority, who links to you and whether those links help or hurt your rankings.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Total backlinks and referring domains</li>
          <li>Domain authority score</li>
          <li>Toxic or spammy backlinks</li>
          <li>Competitor backlink comparison</li>
          <li>Link building opportunities identified</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">📍</div>
        <h3>Local SEO (Google Maps)</h3>
        <p>Your visibility in Google Maps and local search, critical for any business serving a specific city or area.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Google Business Profile completeness score</li>
          <li>Local citation consistency</li>
          <li>NAP (Name, Address, Phone) accuracy</li>
          <li>Google Maps ranking estimate</li>
          <li>Review count and response rate</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="seo-cover-card">
        <div class="seo-cover-icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>Competitor Intelligence</h3>
        <p>What your top 3 ranking competitors are doing that you're not, specific, actionable gaps you can close.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Competitor keyword advantage</li>
          <li>Content gap analysis</li>
          <li>Backlink advantage comparison</li>
          <li>Technical SEO comparison</li>
          <li>Opportunities they've missed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 4: HOW IT WORKS
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-hiw reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Simple Process</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your SEO Audit in 3 Steps</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">No technical setup required. No Search Console access needed. Just your website URL and we take it from there.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="seo-hiw-steps">
      <div class="seo-hiw-step">
        <div class="seo-hiw-num">1</div>
        <div class="seo-hiw-content">
          <h3>Submit Your Website URL</h3>
          <p>Fill in the form above with your name, contact details, website URL, and (optionally) 3 keywords you want to rank for. If you have a competitor URL, add that too, it makes the audit much more actionable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-hiw-connector"></div>
      <div class="seo-hiw-step">
        <div class="seo-hiw-num">2</div>
        <div class="seo-hiw-content">
          <h3>We Analyse Your Site</h3>
          <p>Our team runs a 30-point SEO review covering technical health, keyword rankings, on-page optimisation, local SEO, and your top competitor's advantages. No automated reports, every audit is manually reviewed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-hiw-connector"></div>
      <div class="seo-hiw-step">
        <div class="seo-hiw-num">3</div>
        <div class="seo-hiw-content">
          <h3>Receive Your PDF Report</h3>
          <p>Within 48 hours, you receive a detailed PDF. Every finding is rated by impact (high, medium, low), explained plainly, and given a specific fix recommendation. Priority action list included.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 5: BEFORE / AFTER
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-results reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">After Acting on the Audit</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">What Happens When Businesses Fix the Issues We Find</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="before-after-grid">
      <div class="ba-card">
        <div class="ba-label">Before Audit</div>
        <div class="ba-business">Dental Clinic · Satellite, Ahmedabad</div>
        <div class="ba-metrics">
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--bad">
            <strong>Page 5+</strong>
            <span>Google ranking</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--bad">
            <strong>3</strong>
            <span>Monthly leads</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--bad">
            <strong>42</strong>
            <span>SEO score</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-issues">
          <p>Key issues found: GBP not claimed, homepage noindex tag from plugin, no keyword-optimized service pages, 14 broken image alt tags, 0 local citations</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ba-arrow">→</div>

      <div class="ba-card ba-card--after">
        <div class="ba-label">6 Months After</div>
        <div class="ba-business">Same Clinic · Post-Implementation</div>
        <div class="ba-metrics">
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--good">
            <strong>Page 1</strong>
            <span>Google ranking</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--good">
            <strong>28</strong>
            <span>Monthly leads</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ba-metric ba-metric--good">
            <strong>87</strong>
            <span>SEO score</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ba-outcome">
          <p>"The audit identified 11 issues. We fixed 8 ourselves and hired DC technolabs for the rest. Best business decision we made this year."</p>
          <span>, Dr. Kruti Patel, Bodakdev</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 6: WHO IS THIS FOR
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-wif reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">Is This Right For You?</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Who Gets the Most Value From This Audit</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="seo-wif-grid">
      <div class="seo-wif-card">
        <div class="seo-wif-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Businesses That Can't Find Themselves on Google</h3>
        <p>You search for your service in Ahmedabad and your competitors appear but you don't. The audit pinpoints exactly which ranking factors are missing and which competitors you need to beat.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-wif-card">
        <div class="seo-wif-icon">📉</div>
        <h3>Businesses Whose Organic Traffic Dropped Suddenly</h3>
        <p>A Google algorithm update, a site migration, or a plugin change may have caused a ranking drop. The audit identifies the exact cause so you can recover your lost positions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-wif-card">
        <div class="seo-wif-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Businesses Spending on Ads Because SEO Isn't Working</h3>
        <p>If you're paying ₹20,000 to ₹80,000 per month in Google Ads because organic rankings don't bring leads, the audit shows you what to fix so you can reduce ad dependency over time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-wif-card">
        <div class="seo-wif-icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>Businesses That Want to Outrank a Specific Competitor</h3>
        <p>Add their URL in the form and we'll include a side-by-side comparison in your audit, showing exactly what they're doing in SEO that you aren't, and a specific plan to close the gap.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 7: WHY FREE
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-why-free reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="seo-why-free-inner">
      <div class="seo-why-content">
        <span class="section-label">Transparency</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Is This SEO Audit Free?</h2>
        <p>A fair question, and we think it deserves a straight answer.</p>
        <p>We offer free SEO audits because showing you what we find is far more persuasive than telling you what we can do. A detailed, honest audit report demonstrates our expertise in 48 hours in a way no sales call ever could.</p>
        <p>Some businesses use the report to fix issues themselves or pass it to another agency. That is completely fine. We'd rather help your business improve than hide knowledge behind a paid proposal.</p>
        <p>Businesses that hire us after receiving the audit tend to be our best long-term clients, because the relationship starts with proof, not promises. That's the approach we've built over 7 years in Ahmedabad.</p>
        <p>No obligation. No cold calls. No automated follow-up unless you ask for one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="seo-why-callout">
        <div class="seo-why-callout-inner">
          <div class="seo-why-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Our Commitment to You</h3>
          <ul class="seo-why-list">
            <li>Honest findings, good news and bad</li>
            <li>Competitor comparison included free</li>
            <li>No upselling inside the report</li>
            <li>No cold calls if you don't want them</li>
            <li>Your data never shared with anyone</li>
            <li>Delivered within 48 hours, every time</li>
            <li>Written in plain language throughout</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#seo-audit-form" class="btn btn-primary">Get My Free SEO Audit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 8: TESTIMONIALS
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="seo-audit-testimonials reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header centered">
      <span class="section-label">What Business Owners Say</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">After Receiving Their SEO Audit</h2>
    </div>
